Image Prompt:
Create an ethereal and majestic depiction of God incarnate as described in Christian theology. Visualize a radiant figure cloaked in divine light, standing amidst swirling clouds with outstretched arms symbolizing love and compassion. Include subtle elements like a dove representing the Holy Spirit and a crown signifying divine authority. The scene should evoke a sense of awe and reverence, capturing the profound mystery of the incarnation within Christian beliefs.
